@startuml auth-flow
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor User

User -> Remix: Visit /auth/:authRoute
Remix -> Loader: load(params)
Loader -> Remix: return authRoute

User -> Remix: Submit Form (POST)
Remix -> Action: action(request, params)

Action -> Zod: validate(formData)
Zod --> Action: valid/invalid

Action -> Helpers: handleSignIn/handleSignUp
Helpers -> Backend: fetch(login/register)
Backend --> Helpers: user + Set-Cookie or error

Helpers --> Action: result
Action --> Remix UI: {success|errors} (+ cookie header)

Remix UI -> Browser: Redirect on success
@enduml
